The paper discusses the development of a deep learning vision system for soccer playing humanoid robots, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the development of team play strategies, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY). The use of deep learning in the vision system suggests that the paper may also fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG).
